{{GOCE|date=October 12, 2013}}

== narrow scope - merge? ==

The scope of this article is rather narrow, and it looks like a fork of [[Operation Coast-91]], but one that doesn't expand sufficiently on it so as to satisfy the requirements for standalone articles. There seems to be some standalone coverage of the events at Šibenik, but not much, and one source explicitly equates the titles: ''[http://www.domovinskirat.hr/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=589:-obala-q91q-&catid=106:vojne-operacije-agresora-&Itemid=121 Obala "91" - Ova akcija Jugovojske je poznata i kao bitka za Šibenik odnosno "Rujanski rat".]''. So right now I don't see why this couldn't be a redirect to the Šibenik section of the more general article. --[[User:Joy|Joy &#91;shallot&#93;]] ([[User talk:Joy|talk]]) 10:02, 28 January 2011 (UTC)

[http://www.novi-tjednik.hr/aktualnosti/aktualnosti/6013-daljni-ustroj-postrojbi-113-brigade-ustroj-policije-do-osnivanja-zng-a-i-prvi-vei-oruani-sukob.html This source] also illustrates how the military operations in the area at the time were hardly limited to the six-day assault on Šibenik itself, but that it was all part of the larger scheme. --[[User:Joy|Joy &#91;shallot&#93;]] ([[User talk:Joy|talk]]) 10:05, 28 January 2011 (UTC)

